#: ../../campaigns/emp01.wmf/elemental:9
msgid ""
"After losing an important battle against the barbarians which lead to the "
"loss of a big part of the Empire's territory, Lutius leaves Fremil to start "
"a new life. But his destiny takes his ship into a heavy storm, which nearly "
"destroys it. Only with a lot of luck he manages to beach his damaged ship on "
"an unknown desert strand and save his people. For now."
msgstr ""
"Después de perder una importante batalla contra los bárbaros esto provoca la "
"pérdida de una gran parte del territorio del Imperio, Lutius deja Fremil "
"para iniciar una nueva vida. Pero el destino toma a su barco en una tormenta "
"en el que casi naufraga. Sólo con mucha suerte se las arregla para llegar a "
"una playa con su nave dañada en un desierto desconocido y salvar así a su "
"pueblo. Por ahora."

